## Container Health

```elixir
containers = MetricsDashboard.container_metrics()

container_rows = Enum.map(containers.containers, fn c ->
  health_emoji = case c.health do
    :healthy -> "✅"
    :unhealthy -> "❌"
    :unknown -> "❓"
  end
  "| #{c.name} | #{c.status} | #{c.port} | #{health_emoji} #{c.health} |"
end)

Kino.Markdown.new("""
### Container Status

| Container | Status | Port | Health |
|-----------|--------|------|--------|
#{Enum.join(container_rows, "\n")}

**Overall Health**: #{containers.overall_health}
""")
```

