## Session Information

```elixir
session = Dashboard.session_info()

Kino.Markdown.new("""
### Current Session

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Running | #{session.running} |
| Session ID | #{session.session_id || "N/A"} |
| Started At | #{session.started_at || "N/A"} |
| Operators | #{length(session.operators || [])} |
| Pending Authorizations | #{session.pending_authorizations || 0} |
""")
```

