## Quick Actions

```elixir
Kino.Markdown.new("""
### Available Commands

**Safety**
- `Guardian.status()` - Get Guardian status
- `Envelope.health_check(%{})` - Check envelope health
- `DeadMansSwitch.state()` - Get DMS state
- `DeadMansSwitch.heartbeat(:manual)` - Send manual heartbeat

**Dashboard**
- `Dashboard.system_status()` - Full system status
- `Dashboard.safety_status()` - Safety subsystem status
- `Dashboard.resource_status()` - Resource utilization

**Metrics**
- `MetricsDashboard.beam_metrics()` - BEAM VM metrics
- `MetricsDashboard.flame_metrics()` - FLAME pool status
- `MetricsDashboard.agent_metrics()` - Agent status
""")
```
